<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>jié bào pín pín chuán jiā yīn 迦南235</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fān shān yuè lǐng bá shān shè shuǐ kàn dào yī kē kē xuān jiào de xīn
 qiān lǐ tiáo tiáo bù wèi jiān xīn, zǒu lái wú shù míng xuān jiào de rén
 zài tiān yá zài hǎi jiǎo, zài chéng yì zài xiāng cūn
 yǒu zhǒng zi yǒu gān lín jié bào pín pín chuán jiā yīn.</lyrics>
</song>